description: Ranch boss Xavier Cole can always find a use for a good set of helping hands, especially when they belong to such a ripped stud like Roman Todd. Xavier definitely likes what he sees from Roman, and has all kinds of ideas of how to put this buckin' bronco to work on the ranch. Luckily for him, this ranch hand has hidden talents that run deep... very deep, as Xavier is soon to find out for himself. Being the boss has it's privileges, yahoo!Enjoy!
title: Ranch Hands
